Package: tmg
Type: Package
Title: Truncated Multivariate Gaussian Sampling
Version: 0.1
Date: 2012-08-20
Author: Ari Pakman
Maintainer: Ari Pakman <ari@stat.columbia.edu>
Description: Random number generation of truncated multivariate
        Gaussian distributions using Hamiltonian Monte Carlo. The
        truncation is defined using linear and/or quadratic
        polynomials.
License: GPL-2
Depends: Rcpp (>= 0.9.13), RcppEigen (>= 0.3.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
URL: http://arxiv.org/abs/1208.4118
